APPLE ISSUE - KAFKA LOGS - running out of disk space 


Solution 
========

stop the contrail-svc-monitor 


Steps:
---------
stop kafka service
Modify these parameters in /usr/share/kafka/config/server.porperties
log.cleanup.policy = delete
log.retention.bytes=250000000
log.segment.bytes=250000000
log.retention.hours=24
Check for zookeeper cluster status, 
Restart.       Service kafka start ; service alarm-gen restart; service analytics-api restart
